Yawan kamuwa da cutar korona (Covid-19) a cikin EU/EEA da UK, daga 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020
Yawan kamuwa da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) ya nuna irin wannan yanayin a cikin EU/EEA da UK, wanda ke nuna cewa duk da cewa matakin ya bambanta dangane da ƙasa, annobar COVID-19 tana ƙaruwa cikin sauri a cikin ƙasashe.
Bisa ga kwarewar Italiya, ya kamata ƙasashe, asibitoci da kuma cibiyoyin kula da marasa lafiya su ƙara shiri don ƙara yawan marasa lafiya na COVID-19 waɗanda za su buƙaci kula da lafiya, musamman na ICU.
A ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019, an bayar da rahoton tarin cututtukan huhu na rashin sanannun cututtuka a birnin Wuhan, lardin Hubei, a kasar Sin.
A ranar 9 ga watan Janairun 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka ta kasar Sin ta ce, sabon kwayar cutar coronavirus da ake kira SARS-CoV-2 ya haifar da cutar.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, cutar da SARS-CoV-2 ke haifarwa an kira ta cutar coronavirus (COVID-19).
Bayani har zuwa yanzu shine kusan kashi 80 cikin ɗari na mutanen da ke da COVID-19 suna da rashin lafiya mai sauƙi, wato suna da kamuwa da cutar numfashi tare da alamomi ko babu alamomi, kuma yawancin waɗannan suna murmurewa.
A cikin kusan kashi 14 cikin ɗari, kamuwa da COVID-19 ya kara muni zuwa rashin lafiya mai tsanani da ke buƙatar asibiti yayin da sauran kashi 6 cikin ɗari ke fama da mummunan cuta da ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani.
Yawan mutuwar marasa lafiya da ke asibiti saboda COVID-19 ya kai kusan kashi 4 cikin ɗari.
A cikin wannan binciken, an kimanta yanayin ƙididdigar COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa a cikin EU/EEA da UK kuma an kwatanta su da na lardin Hubei, China.
Mun kuma kwatanta adadin masu kamuwa da COVID-19 a EU/EEA da UK da adadin da aka samu a Italiya tsakanin 31 ga Janairu da 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU/AEA da United Kingdom
Bayan abin da ya faru a China, COVID-19 ya bazu sosai a duniya kuma yana bin sahun sauran ƙasashe a duniya.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Darakta Janar na Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
A cikin fitowar EuroSurveillance na 5 ga Maris, 2020, Spiteri da sauransu sun ba da rahoton farkon tabbacin cutar COVID-19 ta Turai bisa ga ma'anar WHO.
A cikin EU/AEA, an ba da rahoton farkon lokuta uku da Faransa ta tabbatar a ranar 24 ga Janairu, 2020 ga mutanen da suka dawo daga Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
Tun daga ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, an gano shari'o'in COVID-19 a duk ƙasashen EU / EEA 30 da Ingila (UK), inda tsakanin 31 ga Disamba, 2019 zuwa wannan ranar, an ba da rahoton shari'o'i 39,768 da mutuwar 1,727, tare da shari'o'i 17,750 da mutuwar 1,441 a Italiya kadai.
Samun ƙididdigar yawan adadin masu kamuwa da COVID-19
Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC) tana sabunta adadin masu cutar COVID-19 da aka ruwaito a kowace ƙasa a duniya, wanda aka samo daga kafofin hukuma kawai kamar ma'aikatar lafiya ta ƙasar, hukumomin kiwon lafiya na ƙasa da na yanki da WHO, kowace rana da ƙarfe 8:00.
An yi amfani da wannan bayanan don kimanta yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU/AEA da United Kingdom da kuma kwatanta su da na Italiya.
A matsayin ma'auni na yaduwar cututtukan COVID-19, mun lissafa yawan adadin cututtukan COVID-19 a cikin kwanaki 14, sannan kuma mun yi la'akari da yanayin COVID-19, a duk ƙasashen EU/AEA da Ingila, tsakanin Janairu 1 da Maris 15, 2020.
Mun kuma ba da adadin adadin cututtukan da aka ruwaito daga kowace ƙasa daga 15 ga Maris, 2020 da ƙarfe 8:00 na safe, idan aka kwatanta da adadin a Italiya tsakanin 31 ga Janairu da 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU/AEA da UK
Hanyoyin da aka samu na yawan masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a cikin kwanaki 14 a cikin EU/EEA da UK sun bi na lardin Hubei (China) (Figure 1).
Ga EU/AEA da UK gabaɗaya, yawan adadin COVID-19 ya fara ƙaruwa a kusan 21 ga Fabrairu, sannan ya ƙaru sosai a kusan 28 ga Fabrairu, 2020 (Mataki na gaba).
Wannan ya fi yawaita ne saboda saurin karuwar adadin masu kamuwa da cutar da aka ruwaito daga Italiya, amma duk ƙasashen EU/AEA da Ingila sun nuna irin wannan karuwar adadin COVID-19 (ƙarin bayani).
Hoto na 2 ya nuna adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Ingila idan aka kwatanta da Italiya a tsakanin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Ya nuna cewa tun daga ranar 15 ga Maris da ƙarfe 8:00 na safe, wasu ƙasashe 15 na EU / EEA da Burtaniya sun ba da rahoton jimlar adadin shari'o'in da suka riga sun yi daidai da na Italiya makonni 3 da suka gabata ko ƙasa da haka.
Sakamakon bincikenmu ya nuna cewa adadin masu kamuwa da COVID-19 da aka ruwaito suna ƙaruwa cikin sauri a EU/AEA da UK.
Hanyoyin da ake gani a cikin adadin COVID-19 sun nuna cewa annobar tana ƙaruwa da sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Wannan duk da cewa ƙasashe suna cikin matakai daban-daban, duk da bambancin amsoshin lafiyar jama'a na ƙasa, yiwuwar bambancin ma'anar yanayin a cikin ƙasashe da kuma ladabi daban-daban don zaɓar marasa lafiya da za a gwada su don tabbatar da cutar COVID-19, gami da gwajin biye.
A farkon watan Maris na 2020, likitoci a yankunan da cutar ta shafa a Italiya sun bayyana halin da ake ciki inda kusan kashi 10 cikin 100 na marasa lafiyar COVID-19 ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani kuma kafofin watsa labarai sun ba da rahoton cewa asibitoci da raka'a kulawa mai tsanani a waɗannan yankuna sun riga sun kai iyakar ƙarfin su.
A halin yanzu akwai bayanai game da asibitoci da/ko cibiyoyin kulawa na musamman na COVID-19 a cikin EU/AEA don kashi 6% da 1% na shari'o'in bi da bi (ba a nuna bayanai ba).
Duk da haka, dole ne a tattara su ta hanyar da ta dace don haɓaka bayanan sa ido na yanzu wanda ke mai da hankali kan yawan adadin rahotanni da yawan mutuwar.
Wani bincike da aka yi a shekara ta 2010-11 ya nuna cewa akwai bambanci sosai a wuraren kula da marasa lafiya a Turai, daga wurare 29.2 a Jamus zuwa wurare 4.2 a Portugal.
Wannan yana nufin cewa ƙasashe na iya samun ƙarin ko ƙasa da albarkatun Italiya (gadoje 12.5 na kulawa mai tsanani da kulawa ta matsakaici ga mutane 100,000 a 201011).
Ana samun yanayin samfurin da ya danganci wadatar kiwon lafiya, tare da kimantawa ga kowace ƙasa ta EU/EEA da UK na yaduwar COVID-19 da aka kwantar da su a asibiti da ke da alaƙa da haɗarin &gt; 90% na wucewar ƙarfin gadaje na ICU, a cikin sabuntawa na shida na ƙimar haɗarin gaggawa na COVID-19 na CTE.
Tun da yake har yanzu an tattara lokuta a yankuna na EU / EEA da UK, asibitoci da cibiyoyin kulawa da hankali suna ba da sabis ga takamaiman al'ummomin yanki, ana son samar da bayanai game da lokuta da gadaje masu kulawa a matakin SUN 2 (NTS-2).
Kwarewar Italiya da kuma abubuwan da ke faruwa a wasu ƙasashe sun nuna cewa annobar COVID-19 tana ƙaruwa cikin sauri a cikin EU/AEA da United Kingdom.
Don haka, dole ne ƙasashe, asibitoci da cibiyoyin kulawa da keɓaɓɓu su shirya kansu don yanayin ci gaba na SARS-CoV-2 da kuma ƙaruwar yawan marasa lafiyar COVID-19 da ke buƙatar kulawa ta kiwon lafiya, musamman kulawa mai tsanani, kamar wannan da ke faruwa a yankunan da cutar ta shafa a Italiya.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a cikin ƙididdigar haɗarin gaggawa na CDC, tsarin gabaɗaya mai saurin gaba yana da mahimmanci don jinkirta yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 yayin da ake canzawa daga hanyar hanawa zuwa ragewa, saboda ƙididdigar ƙaruwa cikin sauri na ƙwayoyin cuta na iya ba masu yanke shawara da asibitoci isasshen lokaci don fahimta, karɓa da daidaita amsar su idan ba a aiwatar da su ba a gaba.
Ƙididdigar haɗarin gaggawa ta kuma lissafa matakan kiwon lafiya na jama'a don rage tasirin annobar.
Akwai iyakantaccen damar da ƙasashe za su iya ƙara ƙarfin sarrafawa don rage yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 da rage matsin lamba kan kiwon lafiya.
Idan hakan bai yi nasara ba, tsarin kiwon lafiya a sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA na iya fuskantar ƙaruwar yawan marasa lafiya da ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani a cikin kwanaki ko makonni masu zuwa.
