Waɗannan ƙwayoyin cuta suna da mafi girman kwayoyin halitta tsakanin ƙwayoyin cuta masu ƙwayoyin cuta na RNA, suna da kilo 26 zuwa 32 kuma ana kiran su "ƙwayoyin cuta na kambi" saboda tsarin su kamar kambi ne a ƙarƙashin na'urar bincike.
A cikin tsarin kwayoyin halitta, coronaviruses suna da kwayoyin halitta marasa rarrabuwa waɗanda ke da tsari iri ɗaya.
Kimanin kashi biyu bisa uku na kwayoyin halitta suna da manyan nau'ikan buɗe-karanta masu haɗuwa (ORF1a da ORF1b), waɗanda ke canzawa zuwa nau'ikan ƙwayoyin cuta masu yawa pp1a da pp1ab.
Ana kuma sarrafa sunadarai masu yawa don samar da sunadarai 16 marasa tsari, wanda ake kira nsp1~16.
Sauran ɓangaren kwayoyin halitta yana ɗauke da samfuran buɗewar furotin na tsarin, ciki har da Spike S, Sheath E, membrane M, da kuma DNA protein N.
Ƙari ga haka, ƙwayoyin cuta na corona iri dabam-dabam suna ɗauke da wasu sunadarai na musamman.
Bisa ga bambancin jerin sunayen sunadarai, an rarraba coronaviruses zuwa nau'ikan hudu (alpha coronavirus, beta coronavirus, gamma coronavirus, da delta coronavirus), daga cikinsu akwai nau'ikan beta coronavirus waɗanda suka haɗa da yawancin coronavirus na ɗan adam kuma an raba su zuwa nau'ikan hudu (A, W, C, D).
Shaidar juyin halitta ta nuna cewa jemage da kuma kwari suna aiki a matsayin asalin kwayoyin halitta na yawancin coronaviruses alpha da beta, yayin da tsuntsaye sune babban kantin kayan ajiya na coronaviruses gamma da delta.
A cikin dubban shekaru, coronaviruses sun ci gaba da ƙetare shingen jinsuna kuma wasu daga cikinsu sun zama masu haifar da cututtukan mutane masu tsanani.
An san nau'in cutar korona guda bakwai.
Daga cikin su akwai cutar coronavirus ta mutum 229E da kuma cutar coronavirus ta mutum-NL63, waɗanda ke cikin rukunin alpha.
Sauran kwayoyin cutar beta guda biyar sun haɗa da cutar OC43, HKU1, SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV, da SARS-CoV-2.
Kwayar cutar coronavirus-229E, OC43, HKU1, da NL63 yawanci suna haifar da alamun rashin lafiya, kamar sanyi ko zawo ko duka biyun.
