An ware kwayar cutar coronavirus ta mutum 229E, nau'in farko B814, daga ɓoyayyen hanci na marasa lafiya da mura a tsakiyar shekarun 1960.
Tun daga lokacin an tattara bayanai da yawa ta hanyar nazarin cutar HCoV-229E da HCoV-OC43, waɗanda ke warkar da alamun cutar ta atomatik.
A gaskiya, an yarda da cewa kamuwa da cutar coronavirus ba ta da lahani har sai SARS ya ɓarke.
Cutar SARS ta 2003 ta kasance daga cikin cututtuka mafi muni a tarihinmu, inda mutane 8,000 suka kamu da cutar tare da kusan kashi 10 cikin 100 na mutuwar.
Shekaru goma bayan haka, cutar MERS ta Gabas ta Tsakiya ta sake barkewa, ta zama babbar annoba a yankin Larabawa, kuma ta bazu zuwa sauran duniya.
Sabuwar cutar coronavirus ta mutum ta 2019 (HCoV-2019), wacce aka sake masa suna SARS-CoV-2, ita ce sanadin cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19), wacce ta kashe mutane sama da 3,120 kuma ta kamu da mutane sama da 91,000 a ranar 3 ga Maris, 2020.
An yi gargadi kuma dole ne duniya ta shirya don fuskantar barkewar cutar SARS-CoV-2.
Dukkanin kwayoyin cutar corona guda bakwai na mutum sun samo asali ne daga dabbobi kamar su barawo, beraye, ko kuma dabbobin gida.
Akwai shaidu da yawa da ke nuna cewa dukkanin kwayar cutar coronavirus ta ɗan adam ta samo asali ne daga jemage, inda ƙwayoyin cuta ke da kyau kuma ba sa haifar da cuta amma suna nuna bambancin kwayoyin halitta.
Cutar COVID-19 ta haifar da kalubale na kiwon lafiya, kimiyya, zamantakewa, da ɗabi'a ga China da duniya.
Binciken asalin dabbobi na coronavirus na mutum ya nuna tsarin fahimtar tarihin halitta, abubuwan motsawa da abubuwan da ke hana motsi tsakanin jinsuna.
Wannan zai iya jagorantar ko sauƙaƙa binciken mai ajiya, mai watsa shiri na tsakiya da kuma dabba mai karɓar baƙi don SARS-CoV-2, tare da mahimman tasiri don hana tasirin gaba.
A wannan bita mun ba da cikakken bayyani game da asalin dabbobi, sauyawa tsakanin nau'ikan halittu, da kuma cutar da ke haifar da cutar coronavirus.
Musamman, muna haskakawa da tattauna yarda da cewa kwayar cutar kwayar cutar coronavirus ta mutum ba ta haifar da cututtuka a cikin masu ba da gudummawar ta halitta amma ta zama mai cutarwa bayan an canza ta tsakanin jinsuna zuwa sabon mai ba da kyauta.
Muna kuma nazarin kimantawar hanyar cutar coronavirus ta mutum inda yawan kamuwa da cutar yakan kasance tare da rage yawan kamuwa da cutar.
A wannan mahallin, muna kuma tattauna sakamakon barkewar cutar SARS-CoV-2.
An san coronavirus na dabbobi tun daga ƙarshen 1930s.
Kafin a fara ware kwayar B814 na kwayar cutar coronavirus ta 229E daga ɓoyayyen hanci na marasa lafiya masu sanyi, an ware nau'ikan coronaviruses daban-daban daga dabbobi daban-daban da ke fama da cutar, gami da turkey, beraye, shanu, aladu, kuliyoyi, da karnuka.
A cikin shekarun da suka gabata, an gano nau'ikan coronaviruses guda bakwai.
