Kwayar cutar HCoV-229E da HCoV-OC43 sun bazu a duniya, kuma galibi suna yin yaduwa a lokacin hunturu a cikin yanayin zafi.
A yadda aka saba, lokacin haifuwar waɗannan ƙwayoyin cuta biyu bai kai mako ɗaya ba, sai kuma ji na rashin lafiya na kusan makonni biyu.
A cewar wani bincike da aka yi a kan mutane, kamuwa da cutar HCoV-229E a cikin mutane masu lafiya ya haifar da sanyi mai sauƙi.
Wasu marasa lafiya da ke fama da rashin rigakafi sun nuna mummunan rauni a cikin ƙananan numfashi.
SARS, wanda kuma aka fi sani da "ciwon huhu na rashin lafiya", shine annobar farko da aka fara ganowa a tarihin ɗan adam ta hanyar kwayar cutar coronavirus kuma wanda ya haifar da ita shine SARS-CoV, wanda shine kwayar cutar coronavirus ta uku da aka gano.
An fara samun cutar SARS a ƙarshen shekara ta 2002 a lardin Guangdong na ƙasar Sin.
Cutar SARS ta haifar da kamuwa da cutar 8,096 da mutuwar 774, kuma ta bazu cikin ƙasashe da nahiyoyi da yawa.
Ba tare da la'akari da mai ɗaukar hoto ba, an kiyasta cewa kamuwa da cuta guda ɗaya na iya haifar da kusan kamuwa da cuta biyu, tare da lokacin ɗaukar ciki na kwanaki 4 zuwa 7 da kuma ƙaruwa na ƙwayoyin cuta a ranar 10 na cutar.
Alamun SARS-CoV sun fara da ciwon tsoka, ciwon kai, zazzabi, rashin lafiya, da jin tsoro, kuma suna biyo baya da wahalar numfashi, tari da kuma numfashi.
Rashin ƙwayoyin lymph, rashin aiki na hanta, da haɓaka kwayar halitta sune cututtukan da aka saba da su a cikin SARS.
An kuma lura a cikin marasa lafiya na SARS da lalacewar gemu, haɓakar ƙwayoyin cuta, da ƙaruwa da ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin cuta.
Kimanin kashi 20 zuwa 30 cikin 100 na marasa lafiya suna bukatar kulawa mai tsanani da kuma numfashi na wucin gadi.
Baya ga ƙananan tsarin numfashi, a cikin mawuyacin yanayi, gabobin da yawa na iya kamuwa da cutar ciki har da narkewar abinci, hanta da koda kuma yawanci ana haɗuwa da guguwar cytokine wanda zai iya zama mai kisa musamman a cikin marasa lafiya marasa lafiya.
An fara gano kwayar cutar ne daga wani mutum da ya kamu da cutar a lokacin da aka yi masa allurar huhu daga wani dangin wanda ya yi tafiya daga Guangzhou zuwa Hong Kong.
Tun daga lokacin, an yi ƙoƙari sosai wajen yin bincike a kan cutar korona.
An ware kwayar cutar coronavirus ta mutum-NL63 daga jariri ɗan wata 7 daga Netherlands a ƙarshen 2004.
Da farko an gano cewa yana da yawa a cikin yara ƙanana, tsofaffi, da marasa lafiya masu cutar HIV da ke fama da cututtukan numfashi.
Cutar sanyi, cututtukan da ke tattare da cutar, zazzabi, da cututtukan ƙwayar cuta sune alamun cututtukan da ke haifar da cutar coronavirus-NL63.
Wani bincike mai zaman kansa ya bayyana yadda aka ware kwayar cutar daga hancin wani yaro mai wata takwas da ke fama da cutar huhu a Netherlands.
