Ko da yake kalmar "annoba" tana nufin yaduwar cutar ne kawai, ba yadda wasu abubuwa ke da hatsari ba, WHO ta yi gargadin bukatar tilasta gwamnatoci su dauki matakan da suka dace:
"Dukkan kasashen duniya na iya canza yanayin annobar.
Darakta Janar na Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya, Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus ya ce: "Idan ƙasashe suka gano kuma suka gwada mutane, suka kula da su, suka ware su, suka bi diddigin yanayin su, kuma suka tattara su don fuskantar su".
"Dukkanmu muna cikin damuwa game da yawan yaduwar cutar da kuma haɗarin da ke tattare da cutar da kuma rashin aikin da ake yi".
Dokta Tom Friedan, tsohon darektan Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka ta Amirka, ya ce wannan annoba "ba ta da misali".
A wata sanarwa da CNN ta wallafa a watan Fabrairu, ya ce, "Babu wata kwayar cutar numfashi da aka gano daga farkon bayyanarta zuwa ci gaba da yaduwa a duniya, sai mura".
Gibrisus ya bayyana irin wannan ra'ayi, yana cewa: "Ba mu taɓa fuskantar annobar da wata kwayar cutar Corona ta haifar ba".
Ya ci gaba: "Ba mu taɓa ganin annoba da za a iya sarrafawa a lokaci ɗaya ba".
An bayyana sabon yanayin a matsayin annoba bayan da Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta yanke shawarar a watan Janairu cewa cutar ta zama gaggawa ta kiwon lafiya da ke haifar da damuwa a duniya.
Dokta Anthony Fauci, darektan Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka ta Amirka, ya ce game da annobar: "Ainihin abin da za a ce shi ne, abubuwa za su daɗa muni".
Kamfanin dillancin labarai na Associated Press ya ruwaito cewa akwai aƙalla mutane 126,000 da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 a duniya tun ranar Alhamis, kuma sama da 4,600 sun mutu.
Cutar kwayar cutar coronavirus ta 2019-20 cuta ce ta cutar kwayar cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (Covid-19), wacce kwayar cutar coronavirus 2 ke haifarwa wacce ke da alaƙa da mummunan cututtukan numfashi (SARS-CoV-2).
An gano barkewar cutar a Wuhan, China, a watan Disamba na 2019, an ayyana ta a matsayin gaggawa ta lafiyar jama'a ta damuwa ta duniya a ranar 30 ga Janairu, 2020, kuma an gane ta a matsayin annoba a ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020.
Tun daga ranar 10 ga Afrilu, 2020, an samu kusan mutane miliyan 1.61 da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 a ƙasashe 210 da yankuna, wanda ya haifar da mutuwar mutane 97,000.
Kimanin mutane 364,000 sun warke.
An kiyasta yawan mutuwar a China ya kai kashi 4 cikin dari, yayin da a duniya ya kai kashi 13.04 cikin dari a Algeria da kashi 0.08 cikin dari a New Zealand.
Alamomin da ake yawan gani a cikin wannan cuta sun haɗa da zazzabi, tari da kuma numfashi.
Ƙari ga haka, yana iya sa mutum ya kamu da ciwon huhu da kuma ciwon numfashi.
Yawancin lokaci, lokaci tsakanin kamuwa da cutar da bayyanar cututtuka yana da kwana biyar, amma zai iya zama daga kwana biyu zuwa goma sha huɗu.
Babu wani rigakafi ko magani da aka sani da zai iya magance cutar.
Maganin farko shi ne magani na taimako da kuma na alamomi. Abubuwan da ake ba da shawara na rigakafi sun haɗa da wanke hannu, rufe baki lokacin tari, nisantawa, lura, da kuma ware waɗanda ake zargi da cutar.
Hukumomi a duk faɗin duniya suna amsa wannan haɗarin ta hanyar ƙuntata tafiye-tafiye, keɓewa, dokar hana fita, sarrafa haɗarin wurin aiki da rufe wuraren aiki.
Wannan annoba ta haifar da rikicewar zamantakewa da tattalin arziki a duniya, jinkirta ko soke abubuwan wasanni, addini, siyasa, da al'adu, da kuma ƙarancin kayayyaki da aka ƙara ta da tashin hankali.
An rufe makarantu da jami'o'i a ƙasashe 193 ko a yankuna, kuma hakan ya shafi kashi 99.4 na ɗaliban duniya.
An samu karuwar rashin gaskiya game da cutar a yanar gizo, kuma an samu rashin adalci da nuna wariyar launin fata da nuna wariya ga Sinawa, da sauran mutanen da ke da asalin Gabas da kudu maso gabashin Asiya, da kuma sauran yankunan da aka samu karuwar masu kamuwa da cutar.
Sakamakon rage yawan tafiye-tafiye da rufe masana'antun masana'antu, an rage gurbataccen iska da fitar da iskar carbon.
Hukumomin kiwon lafiya a birnin Wuhan (babban birnin lardin Hubei), China sun ba da rahoton tarin cututtukan huhu da ba a san dalilin su ba a ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019, kuma an fara binciken a farkon Janairu, 2020.
Yawancin lokuta ana danganta su da kasuwar sayar da abincin teku ta Wuhan, don haka ana tsammanin kwayar cutar ta samo asali ne daga dabbobi.
An san kwayar cutar da ta haifar da barkewar cutar da SARS-CoV-2, sabuwar kwayar cuta da aka gano wacce ke da alaƙa da kwayar cutar corona a cikin jemage, da kwayar cutar corona a cikin abincin tururuwa, da SARS-CoV. Daga baya an gano cewa mutum na farko da ya nuna alamun cutar ya kamu da cutar a ranar 1 ga Disamba, 2019, kuma wannan mutumin ba shi da wata ma'amala ta bayyananniya tare da rukunin kasuwa mai laushi da aka gano daga baya.
Daga cikin rukunin farkon lokuta da aka ruwaito a watan Disamba na 2019, kashi biyu bisa uku sun kasance masu alaƙa da kasuwa.
A ranar 13 ga Maris, 2020, wani rahoto da ba a tabbatar da shi ba wanda jaridar South China Morning Post ta buga ya nuna cewa wani mutum mai shekaru 55 daga lardin Hubei, mai yiwuwa shine farkon lamarin. A ranar 26 ga Fabrairun, 2020, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta ruwaito cewa duk da cewa an samu raguwar sabbin cututtukan da aka ruwaito a kasar Sin, amma sun tashi ba zato ba tsammani a Italiya, Iran da Koriya ta Kudu, inda yawan sabbin cututtukan da ke wajen kasar Sin ya zarce adadin sabbin cututtukan da ke cikinta a karon farko.
Ana iya samun ƙarancin rahoto, musamman a tsakanin waɗanda ke da alamun rashin lafiya.
A ranar 26 ga Fabrairu, an ba da rahoton ƙananan ƙananan lokuta tsakanin matasa, tare da masu shekaru 19 da ƙasa da kashi 2.4% na lokuta a duk duniya. Babban masanin kimiyya na Burtaniya, Patrick Valance, ya kiyasta cewa ana buƙatar kamuwa da kashi 60% na Biritaniya kafin a aiwatar da aikin kiwo mai tasiri.
Yanayin yana nufin yawan mutanen da aka gwada su don COVID-19 kuma aka tabbatar da cutar bisa ga ƙa'idodin hukuma.
Tun daga ranar 23 ga watan Maris, babu wata ƙasa da ta gwada fiye da kashi 3 cikin ɗari na yawanta, kuma ƙasashe da yawa suna da manufofi na doka da suka hana yin gwaji ga waɗanda ke da alamun rashin lafiya, kamar Italiya, Netherlands, Spain da Switzerland.
Wani bincike da aka buga a ranar 16 ga watan Maris ya gano cewa kimanin kashi 86 cikin 100 na masu kamuwa da COVID-19 ba a gano su ba a China, har zuwa ranar 23 ga Janairu, kuma waɗannan marasa kamuwa da cutar sun kasance tushen kamuwa da kashi 79 cikin ɗari na waɗanda aka yi wa rajista.
Wani bincike da aka fitar a ranar 30 ga watan Maris ya nuna cewa adadin masu kamuwa da cutar a Italiya ya fi na da aka samu.
