An tsaurara matakan sarrafa zirga-zirgar jama'a a birane da dama, kuma an kiyasta cewa kimanin mutane miliyan 760 (fiye da rabin yawan jama'a) sun shiga cikin wasu nau'ikan ƙuntatawa. Bayan barkewar cutar a duniya a watan Maris, hukumomin China sun ɗauki tsauraran matakai don hana "kawo" cutar daga wasu ƙasashe.
Alal misali, Beijing ta sanya dokar keɓewa ta kwanaki 14 ga duk wanda ya dawo birnin daga wasu ƙasashe. A ranar 23 ga watan Maris, mutum ɗaya ya kamu da cutar a ƙasar Sin a cikin kwanaki biyar da suka gabata, ta hanyar matafiyi da ke dawowa Guangzhou daga Istanbul.
A ranar 24 ga watan Maris na 2020, Shugaban Majalisar Jiha na kasar Sin Li Keqiang ya ba da sanarwar raguwar yaduwar cututtukan da ke yaduwa a cikin gida da kuma kula da barkewar cutar a kasar Sin.
An sassauta takunkumin tafiye-tafiye a Hubei a ranar, ban da Wuhan, bayan watanni biyu da sanya dokar kulle. Ma'aikatar Harkokin Wajen China ta sanar a ranar 26 ga Maris, 2020 dakatar da shigar da masu biza ko izinin zama daga ranar 28 ga Maris zuwa gaba, ba tare da wani takamaiman bayani game da lokacin da wannan manufar za ta kare ba.
Waɗanda suke son shiga ƙasar Sin za su nemi biza a ofisoshin jakadancin ƙasar Sin.
Gwamnatin kasar Sin ta bukaci kamfanoni da masana'antu da su ci gaba da aiki a ranar 30 ga watan Maris, kuma ta ba da wasu kudade don karfafawa kamfanoni. Majalisar Jiha ta ayyana ranar makoki da za ta fara da minti uku na shiru a ranar 4 ga Afrilu da karfe 10:00, daidai da bikin Qing Ming, kodayake gwamnatin tsakiya ta bukaci iyalai su nuna girmamawa ta yanar gizo ta hanyar nisantar jiki don kauce wa sake barkewar COVID-19.
An tabbatar da yaduwar COVID-19 daga China zuwa Koriya ta Kudu a ranar 20 ga Janairu, 2020.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Kasa ta sanar da karuwar adadin wadanda suka kamu da cutar a ranar 20 ga watan Fabrairu, wanda ya danganta da taron da aka yi a Daegu na wata sabuwar kungiyar addini da ake kira Shincheonji Jesus Church.
Ana zargin cewa mutanen Shincheongji da ke ziyartar Daegu daga Wuhan ne suka haddasa cutar.
Tun daga ranar 22 ga watan Fabrairu, mutane 1,261 ko kusan kashi 13 cikin dari na masu bin coci 9,336 sun ba da rahoton bayyanar cututtuka. Koriya ta Kudu ta sanar da matakan tsaro mafi girma a ranar 23 ga Fabrairu, 2020.
