Nazarin chloroquine da hydroxychloroquine tare da azithromycin ko ba tare da shi ba ya ƙunshi manyan rashi waɗanda suka hana ƙungiyar likitoci karɓar waɗannan magungunan ba tare da ƙarin nazari ba. Oceltaphamvir ba ya hana SARS-CoV-2 a cikin dakin gwaje-gwaje kuma ba shi da sanannen rawar a cikin maganin COVID-19.
